---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Acumatica ERP Services — Implementation, Rescue, Integration"
  description="AcuMaven delivers Acumatica implementation, rescue projects, integration development, and ongoing support for construction, field service, and manufacturing companies."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Services Built for<br/><em>Companies That Can't Get ERP Wrong</em></h1>
      <p>Implementation. Rescue. Integration. Ongoing support. One consultant, full accountability.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Talk to Steve</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Detail -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Every engagement is run by Steve — not delegated to a junior after the sales call.</p>

      <div class="services-detail-grid">

        <!-- Implementation -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="svc-icon">🏗️</div>
          <h3>Acumatica Implementation</h3>
          <p>New deployments for construction, field service, and manufacturing companies. We handle the full project lifecycle — from discovery and data migration through configuration, testing, training, and go-live. Done right the first time means no rescue needed later.</p>
          <p class="svc-clients">Industries: Construction · Field Service · Manufacturing</p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-svc">Talk to Steve →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Rescue -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="svc-icon">🚨</div>
          <h3>Rescue Projects</h3>
          <p>Took a hit on a bad implementation? We take over stalled, failed, or wildly-over-budget Acumatica projects and get them to a working state — fast. We know what consultants get wrong because we've fixed their work. We also know the fastest path out.</p>
          <p class="svc-clients">Most partners won't touch someone else's broken implementation. We built a practice around it.</p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-svc">Let's assess the damage →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Integration -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="svc-icon">🔁</div>
          <h3>Integration Development</h3>
          <p>Your ERP shouldn't be an island. We connect Acumatica to the rest of your tech stack using Celigo, Boomi, and REST API — and we build integrations that hold up in production, not just in the demo. Real-world clients include Conway, AFL, and NVB Playgrounds.</p>
          <p class="svc-clients">Platforms: Celigo · Boomi · REST API · OData · HubSpot · Shopify · Salesforce</p>
          <a href="/celigo" class="btn-svc">See Celigo Integration →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Ongoing Support -->
        <div class="service-detail-card">
          <div class="svc-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Ongoing Support &amp; Optimization</h3>
          <p>We don't disappear after go-live. Post-launch support includes user training, workflow customization, performance tuning, and continuous improvement. When something breaks or the business changes, you call Steve — not a help desk queue.</p>
          <p class="svc-clients">Retainer or as-needed. You choose.</p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-svc">Talk to Steve →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Certifications bar -->
  <section style="background: var(--light);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Built on Real Certifications</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">11 active Acumatica certifications — not a generalist with a badge.</p>
      <div class="cert-grid">
        <div class="cert-item">Construction Business Consultant</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Business Consultant</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Case Management</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Inventory &amp; Order Management</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Fixed Assets</div>
        <div class="cert-item">REST API Integration Developer</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Implementation Project Manager</div>
        <div class="cert-item">OData Integration Developer</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Project Accounting</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Technical Specialist</div>
        <div class="cert-item">Official Celigo Partner</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section>
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2>Ready to talk?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Tell Steve what you're dealing with. You'll get a straight answer — not a sales pitch.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem;">Talk to Steve</a>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted);">Or email: <a href="mailto:steve@acumaveninc.com">steve@acumaveninc.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
